#
#   `rg` uses this file iff $RIPGREP_CONFIG_PATH points to it.
#

# This flag instructs ripgrep to searches case insensitively if the pattern is
# all lowercase. Otherwise, ripgrep will search case sensitively.
--smart-case

# Make a custom `type`, use like `-t web`.
--type-add
web:include:css,html,js,json,svelte,typescript

#   Hyperlinking
#

# https://github.com/enochchau/ripgrep/blob/master/crates/printer/src/hyperlink/aliases.rs
# "default" format is `file://{host}{path}`, but must be opted into per below.
#--hyperlink-format=default

# Enable cmd-clicking to open a file in BBEdit
--hyperlink-format
x-bbedit://open?url=file:///{path}&line={line}&column={column}

# Uncomment to add (non-default) column numbers in addition to the default line
# numbers. Required to hyperlink to a line and column (by clicking on the column
# number).
#--column
